⭐ ONE-LINE DEFINITIONS (Most important part)

🟦 TOOL CALLING

LLM decides:

“Do I need a tool? Which one? With what arguments?”

🟩 AGENT

A smarter system that uses tool calling + planning + reasoning

to solve multi-step tasks dynamically.

🟥 WORKFLOW / PIPELINE

A fixed sequence of steps defined by the developer, NOT the LLM.

